Don’t get discouraged by haters, do your thing, because in the end all that matters is, that you love what you do. item.description:
Bolteh:

It’s shit.

I wonder if Garry ever woke up saying to himself “Hey, I feel like making a mod for a great game that allows mentally retarded people to create absolutely worthless crap and share it on YouTube”.

For every decent video made with Garry’s mod (Accursed Farm), there’s at least a thousand terribad ones (the videos of yours + an entire legion of failed abortions).

Give people ability to create anything they want - Sturgeon’s law kicks in. Crud everywhere.
